# Per-machine fish settings for gMacBook (matches `hostname -s`).
#
# Loaded by ../config.fish after conf.d/ runs. Use this file for anything that
# is specific to *this* machine: PATH adjustments, machine-only env vars,
# overrides of values set in conf.d/, etc.
#
# This file replaces both the old `~/.zshrc-local` mechanism and any need for
# a separate `fish-local.fish` layer.
#
# Add as needed, e.g.:
#   set -gx SOMETHING_HOME /opt/something
#   fish_add_path -gP /opt/something/bin
